{"tid":927843,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"[居屋客回流、貿易戰緩和] 沙一減至458萬。慧景軒跌破9000/呎","createTime":"2018-12-04T12:16:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-04T15:13:09.000Z","uid":62935,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d17e79ec0776bd5795a37e5a5d8d5c20524634b","tid":927843,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T12:16:05.000Z","msg":"沙田第一城2房減至458.3萬元易手  3年升值14%<br />\n<a href=\"https://ps.hket.com/article/2222926/沙田第一城2房減至458.3萬元易手\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2222926%2F%E6%B2%99%E7%94%B0%E7%AC%AC%E4%B8%80%E5%9F%8E2%E6%88%BF%E6%B8%9B%E8%87%B3458.3%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%E6%98%93%E6%89%8B&d=wy78JA13ImWpYiwIp9yh85WUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=af1e8064\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://ps.hket.com/article/2222926/沙田第一城2房減至458.3萬元易手</a>  3年升值14%?mtc=90025<br />\n<br />\n近期樓市吹淡風，個別業主趁SSD期鬆綁即沽貨。世紀21奇豐物業愉翠苑分行區域經理吳元利表示，新近錄得沙田第一城成交，為48座高層E室，實用面積284平方呎，2房1廳間隔，望園景。單位放盤3個月，原開價535萬元，減價76.7萬元，獲上車客以458.3萬元承接，實用面積呎價16,137元，屬市價。<br />\n<br />\n原業主於2015年11月購入上址，當時作價403萬元，持貨3年滿SSD期沽售，帳面獲利55.3萬元，單位升值14%。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;&mdash;-<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n中原伍耀祖表示，<span style=\"color: red;\">天水圍交投氣氛回升，主要是業主肯減價，議幅有機會多於10%</span>，本月首4天全區已錄20宗住宅成交，較11月同期倍增，其中慧景軒剛連錄兩宗成交個案。<br />\n<br />\n他指出，其中1座低層G室，實用面積654方呎，三房套房間隔，以585萬港元成交，呎價8,945元，料為屋苑約半年呎價低位。<br />\n<br />\n另一宗買賣為1座高層C室，實用面積555方呎，兩房間隔，以573萬元獲買家承接，呎價10,324元。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n居屋客回流左一個weekend、貿易戰緩和左一日<br />\n升交大增<br />\n不過係劈價成交"},{"pid":"ac27827482fa9abf3234c64c796477b278a36950","tid":927843,"uid":83582,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:36:27.000Z","msg":"成交升, 價跌 <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d43b4135905fd4b145df1ffcd541277cc6de8cb5","tid":927843,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:39:59.000Z","msg":"大家都知90日逃生門好快過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eafefac5dd12778ff209cd883360c893408c5f3a","tid":927843,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"02b587ed11089b248ec973dc1e1eced27b977139","tid":927843,"uid":62935,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eafefac5dd12778ff209cd883360c893408c5f3a","tid":927843,"uid":171446,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:41:55.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:11:31.000Z","msg":"花生兄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3a7c47eb7a50425e6d5ce7582446d8b3efd99657","tid":927843,"uid":18012,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d43b4135905fd4b145df1ffcd541277cc6de8cb5","tid":927843,"uid":22839,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T14:39:59.000Z","msg":"大家都知90日逃生門好快過<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/33.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T15:13:09.000Z","msg":"咁買嗰D係咩人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n真係睇唔透"}]}